<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Page Not Found</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            color: #333;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            height: 100vh;
            flex-direction: column;
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: 3em;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        p {
            font-size: 1.2em;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        a {
            color: #007bff;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        a:hover {
            text-decoration: underline;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div>
        <h1>404 - Page Not Found</h1>
        <p>We couldn't find the page you're looking for.</p>
        <p>Please check the URL or go back to <a href="/">homepage</a>.</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
